night_01_F: ^Other figures scuttle by, navigating around the heap.
night_01: ^A homeless person lies on the pavement.
^They are inert, weighed down with mouldering blankets.
^Other people scuttle by, navigating around the heap.
night_02_F: ^There aren't many of them out tonight.
^The ones who are out, seem blurry. Less...real.
night_02: ^You pass a blocked off street. Neon orange gates flare under the fluorescent street lights.
^The ones who are, are solid blocks in your vision.
^Plodding along on their set paths, yet hopelessly immobile.
